title: Anastacia - The Video Collection (DVD-9)
description:
Anastacia - The Video Collection (DVD-9)

Features all of Anastacia&#039; videos (at the end of 2002), plus behind the scenes footage, over 90 minutes of programming. This collection includes all of Anastacia&#039;s videos from her two albums (Not That Kind and Freak Of Nature), as well as the video for Boom - the 2002 FIFA World Cup theme song, and also features never-seen-before behind the scenes footage.
